e entities can hear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493670/extras/b402df3862cc6f818e2eeef1d373823d.poster.avif?t=1739827717\" width=620 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493670/extras/b402df3862cc6f818e2eeef1d373823d.webm?t=1739827717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493670/extras/b402df3862cc6f818e2eeef1d373823d.mp4?t=1739827717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
